snippet.title: Spellsworn Codex Trailer
snippet.description:
The trailer for the recent Codex Update (version 0.5.5)
Spellsworn is a game based on the warlock mod for Warcraft III, and is currently on Steam Early Access.
http://store.steampowered.com/app/360620/

Check it out if you're interested! Or maybe stop by our homepage.
http://www.spellsworn.com
...and social media
www.facebook.com/frogsongstudios
https://twitter.com/FrogsongStudios

Thanks for looking in!
/Frogsong Studios
